1. Individual and team level assessment of technology and technical resource current status in terms of business in hand and business in the pipeline and in line with MD's direction

2. Identifying the risks of the business, technology and technical resources as we are seeing and the steps we are taking and should take to mitigate those risks

3. Identify the steps we must take from HR perspective to align technology and technical resources fully aligned with business direction from MD

4. Finally, set some KPI's to measure our progress against the activities that we might plan during our discussion so that we can measure our achievements and progress in a very clear way
